{"tid":1494559,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬引名句回應批評：有血有肉招人厭","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T16:48:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b66b67bc92fce166d00a5abb4d46a74f5421c6","tid":1494559,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"身陷轉會風波的尼馬近日飽受批評，對此他於twitter上引用牙買加藝術家的名句作回應，指群眾只喜歡「偽人」，對有血有肉的公眾人物卻嗤之以鼻。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎聖日耳門球迷近日把尼馬視為「過街老鼠」，更在比賽時叫這名巴西球星滾出巴黎。對於攻擊尼馬未作正面回應，但在twitter貼上牙買加哥手Bob Marley照片並配上其名句「當一個人活得真實時往往惹人討厭，而活得虛偽則博得大眾喜愛」，似是為自己平反。<br />\n<br />\n隨轉會「死線」逼近，PSG方面也為出售尼馬而著急，早前他們將接受先借後買的方式去讓該巴西球星離隊。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn0%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=584a2c2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"4127a72b97fe62026000c89d9237f2014e460ebe","tid":1494559,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/CorruptSentimentalAsianconstablebutterfly-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FCorruptSentimentalAsianconstablebutterfly-max-1mb.gif&h=889b47c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63020edda9a834f0f573ebddb2bbb426b7991b04","tid":1494559,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/a0211dfd2a397b6abd327a5f72d1fccb/tenor.gif?itemid=12098476\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fa0211dfd2a397b6abd327a5f72d1fccb%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D12098476&h=74c051b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3523dda127c9a277da6e451610835d938788f600","tid":1494559,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"佢本身乞鳩人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/p